text: Knowlton is a census-designated place in the town of Knowlton, Marathon County, Wisconsin, United States. Its population was 120 as of the 2010 census. The northern terminus for Wisconsin Highway 34 is located just north of Knowlton and the highway passes through the community. ==Images== File:Lake Dubay Lions Park Knowlton WI.jpg|Lake DuBay Lions Park at Knowlton File:St. Francis Xavier Catholic Church Knowlton WI.jpg|St. Francis Xavier Catholic Church at Knowlton ==References== Category:Census-designated places in Marathon County, Wisconsin Category:Census-designated places in Wisconsin
